<textBlocks>
	<container id="formVBox">
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="25.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Activity 7: Identify next steps and reflect">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="In this workshop participants discuss potential steps that would need to happen to implement the resilience actions.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Why do this: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Identify a few tangible actions and immediate next steps, as well as lay the groundwork for longer term implementation.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="How to do this: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;As a group, discuss the following:">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- What is one thing people can do walking away from the workshop?">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- Where is there interest in working together? How? Who else might need to be involved?">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- Are there any upcoming opportunities for taking action? What barriers to action might need to be addressed?">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- How should outputs from this workshop be shared more widely? Who needs to be updated?">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;In this conversation, make the distincation clear between when the group is making suggestions for consideration in implementation, and when it is making decisions such as what the final list of 'next steps' will include, who is committing to what, etc.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Before wrapping up the workshop, take some time to reflect with participants about how the process went.">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- What makes you hopeful and what do you still have concerns about?">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- What was the most beneficial part of the process for you? What should be do differently next time?">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
	</container>
